Texts.Chs: 印有绘世者执政委员会会徽的旗帜。
Texts.Eng: A banner with the emblem of the Skath's ruling council imprinted on it.

Texts.Chs: 这面旗帜上有我们这一类的标志，还有四位执政议员。
Texts.Eng: This banner bears the emblem of our kind, along with the four ruling councillors.

Texts.Chs: 这面旗帜上有绘世者的标志。
Texts.Eng: This banner bears the emblem of the Skath.

Texts.Chs: 这个横幅代表了绘世者，以及他们的政府。
Texts.Eng: This banner represents the Skath as a whole, as well as their government.
